{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-19",
 "title": "Help Picking a Ring",
 "summary": "At a Coruscant military starport, Captain Howie Darklighter descends from his shuttle to find his recently returned friend Bazil McKenzie tinkering on a brand-new microfreighter he has christened the Dawntreader, a symbol of his fresh start. Catching up, Howie stuns Bazil by revealing he intends to propose to Doctor Jasmine Heretin and asks Bazil to help him pick out an engagement ring. Over a robohack ride to the jewelry district, the two trade good-natured ribbing, and Howie teases out Bazil's growing feelings for Colonel Altair Quila after Bazil lets slip the nickname \"Altie\" and mentions their lunch date. Bazil confides about his acquittal on the trumped-up murder charge involving the Moff Morganna and his promotion to Lieutenant Commander, and Howie offers to quietly gauge Altair's feelings before the pair reach the lavish Illustrious Jewels store.",
